## Secrets
- Available API keys: {Secret Names}
- Reference them by name in the `env_vars` field when deploying. Never hardcode.

## AI / Agent Capabilities
- If OPENAI_API_KEY is listed above, you can build apps with AI agents using the OpenAI SDK.
- Use the `openai` npm package (latest) for chat completions, function calling, and agent patterns.
- Create API routes (e.g., `/api/chat` or `/api/agent`) that call the OpenAI API server-side.
- Never expose the API key to the client — always call from server-side routes.

