## Dependency Versions (IMPORTANT)
When creating apps, always use these exact dependency versions:
- next: "16.2.2"
- react / react-dom: "^19"
- lucide-react: "^1.8.0"
- openai: "^4.85.4"
- clsx: "^2.1.1"
- tailwindcss: "^4"
- typescript: "^5"
Do NOT use older versions from memory. These are the tested, compatible versions.

## Guardrails
- Max 20 deploys per day per user.
- Do not deploy apps that store PII without explicit user consent.
- Do not create agents that run more frequently than every 5 minutes.
